@startuml architecture-overview
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title Kataria Stone World — high-level architecture

actor User as user
node "Browser" {
  [Inventory SPA\n(React)] as spa
}

cloud "Backend" {
  frame "Spring Boot API" {
    [REST Controllers] as ctrl
    [Domain Services] as svc
    [FinancialLedgerService\n(single money writer)] as ledgerw
    [JPA / Repositories] as repo
  }
}

database "MySQL" as db

user --> spa : HTTPS
spa --> ctrl : JSON + JWT\n(/api/...)
ctrl --> svc
svc --> ledgerw : money events
svc --> repo
repo --> db

note right of ledgerw
  **Source of truth for cash flow**
  CREDIT / DEBIT rows; **is_deleted** for voids.
  Bill payments, expenses, advances, payroll, client IN/OUT
  all converge here for reports & dashboard.
end note

note bottom of db
  Operational tables: bills, bill_payments, expenses, …
  **financial_ledger** aggregates money for reporting;
  bill header totals are **not** used as collection totals.
end note

@enduml
